data.description: Sometimes older homes just have a unique charm all there own. Solidly built with blocks that would make the "Big Bad Wolf" huff and puff and still never be able to blow your house down. 2 good sized bedrooms, a spacious kitchen with open concept to the living room. A bonus room that can be used for an office or any other of your needs. The front yard is fully fenced, the drive way has plenty of parking for RV's, boats or any other toys you may have. The backyard is private and HUGE it comes complete with a hot tub. Fully fenced. The garage has a nice sized workshop with plenty of room to add more space. Located walking distance to the lake and world class fishing. Whether this is your primary home or a weekend getaway you really cannot go wrong.
